    "title": "Nutshell CRM New Features: Sales Teams Love This 2026 Update",
    "excerpt": "Discover Nutshell CRM's latest features for B2B teams—pipeline management, email sequences, and AI-powered automation. Start your free trial today.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
