    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every few months, a software update lands that genuinely changes how teams work. Nutshell CRM just dropped one of those updates—and if you manage a B2B sales team, you'll want to pay attention.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've been tracking Nutshell for a while now. It's always been that rare breed: a CRM that doesn't make you want to throw your laptop out the window. Simple enough for a five-person startup, powerful enough for a 200-seat sales org. But their latest round of features? It pushes the platform into territory that makes the bigger, clunkier CRMs look outdated.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-nutshell-crm"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through what's new, why it matters, and whether ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell CRM",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " deserves a spot in your tech stack.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Just Changed: The Headline Features",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell's 2026 update didn't just sprinkle a few cosmetic tweaks. They rebuilt some core capabilities from the ground up and added features that B2B teams have been requesting for years.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Powered Sales Intelligence",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The biggest shift is Nutshell's new AI layer. Instead of asking you to manually tag leads, score opportunities, or guess which deals need attention, Nutshell now surfaces insights automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what that looks like in practice:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smart Lead Scoring",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Nutshell analyzes engagement patterns—email opens, link clicks, meeting history—and ranks your leads by conversion likelihood. No more guessing who's hot and who's gone cold.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Deal Risk Alerts",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": When a pipeline deal starts showing warning signs (dropped email engagement, missed follow-ups), Nutshell flags it before you lose the opportunity.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Activity Recommendations",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": The system suggests next actions based on what's worked for similar deals in your pipeline. Think of it as a junior sales manager that never sleeps.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This isn't gimmicky AI for the sake of a press release. It's practical intelligence that helps reps focus on the right deals at the right time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Revamped Email Sequences",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Email sequences were already one of Nutshell's strong suits. The new version makes them significantly more flexible:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Conditional Branching",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Sequences now support if/then logic. If a prospect opens email #2 but doesn't click the link, they get a different follow-up than someone who clicked through. This alone saves hours of manual segmentation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A/B Testing Built In",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Test subject lines, send times, and content variations without leaving the sequence builder. Nutshell automatically picks the winner after your defined sample size.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sequence Analytics Overhaul",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": You can now see exactly where prospects drop off, which steps drive replies, and how your sequences compare across team members.",
