        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Nutshell CRM good for small businesses?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Nutshell was designed with small and mid-sized B2B teams in mind. It offers enterprise-level features like pipeline management, email sequences, and AI-powered insights without the complexity or price tag of tools like Salesforce. Most teams get fully set up within a week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What makes Nutshell CRM different from other CRMs?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell hits a sweet spot between simplicity and power. Unlike lightweight CRMs that teams outgrow quickly, or complex platforms that require dedicated admins, Nutshell gives you customizable pipelines, automated email sequences, real-time reporting, and AI-driven lead scoring in an interface that your team will actually enjoy using.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does Nutshell CRM offer a free trial?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Nutshell offers a 14-day free trial with no credit card required. You get full access to all features, including the new AI-powered sales intelligence tools and email sequence builder. It's the best way to see if the platform fits your team's workflow before committing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Nutshell CRM handle complex B2B sales pipelines?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Definitely. Nutshell supports fully customizable pipeline stages, multiple pipelines for different products or regions, and conditional email branching that adapts to prospect behavior. The new deal risk alerts and smart lead scoring features make managing complex, multi-stakeholder sales cycles much more manageable.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
